OL,3,CUK inflation set to rise after Middle
OL,4,CEast conflict pushed up fuel prices
OL,6,FHigher fuel prices are set to have
OL,7,Fdriven an increase in UK inflation
OL,8,Flast month, according to analysts.
OL,10,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,11,F(ONS) will shed further light on how
OL,12,Fthe conflict in the Middle East is
OL,13,Fimpacting on the cost of living for
OL,14,FBritons on Wednesday morning when it
OL,15,Funveils the latest official inflation
OL,16,Fdata.
OL,18,FConsumer Prices Index (CPI) inflation
OL,19,Fis expected to have risen to 3.3% in
OL,20,FMarch, according to a consensus of
OL,21,Fexperts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
