OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776819790
OL,3,CUK inflation set to rise after Middle
OL,4,CEast conflict pushed up fuel prices
OL,6,FIt would push inflation to its highest
OL,7,Flevel since December.
OL,9,FThe Bank of England and most
OL,10,Feconomists have indicated that price
OL,11,Fincreases are set to accelerate in the
OL,12,Fcoming months as the impact of the
OL,13,FMiddle East conflict feeds into the
OL,14,Fcost of products and services.
OL,16,FLast month, the Bank of England
OL,17,Findicated that inflation is likely to
OL,18,Frise to as high as 3.5% by the third
OL,19,Fquarter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
