OL,3,CUK inflation set to rise after Middle
OL,4,CEast conflict pushed up fuel prices
OL,6,FEarlier this month, the International
OL,7,FMonetary Fund (IMF) suggested spiking
OL,8,Fenergy prices could help push UK
OL,9,Finflation towards 4%, double the Bank
OL,10,Fof England's 2% inflation target.
OL,12,FAt the start of the year, the central
OL,13,Fbank had predicted that inflation
OL,14,Fwould dip below the 2% target in April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
