OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776819790
OL,3,CUK inflation set to rise after Middle
OL,4,CEast conflict pushed up fuel prices
OL,6,FHowever, the conflict between US-
OL,7,FIsraeli and Iranian forces since late
OL,8,FFebruary has led to a sharp increase
OL,9,Fin oil and gas prices, while
OL,10,Fdisruption to the Strait of Hormuz
OL,11,Fshipping corridor could hit other
OL,12,Fareas.
OL,14,FThe latest data for March will be the
OL,15,Ffirst set of ONS figures to include
OL,16,Felevated petrol and diesel costs since
OL,17,Fthe start of the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
