PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776819790
OL,3,CUK inflation set to rise after Middle
OL,4,CEast conflict pushed up fuel prices
OL,6,FRAC data from Thursday April 16 showed
OL,7,Fthat the average price of a litre of
OL,8,Fpetrol at UK forecourts was 158.1p,
OL,9,F25p more expensive than when the war
OL,10,Fbegan on February 28.
OL,12,FThe average price of a litre of diesel
OL,13,Fsits at 191.2p, up 49p compared with
OL,14,Fthe start of the war.
OL,16,FEconomists at Oxford Economics said
OL,17,Fthey expect the rise in pump prices to
OL,18,Fadd between 0.2 and 0.3 percentage
OL,19,Fpoints to the rate of inflation in
OL,20,FMarch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
